title: Rory McIlroy, 26, finds golfing supremacy is old news
text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle Rory McIlroy tees off on the 18th hole, during the Fry's.com Pro-Am and practice round a day before the start of the tournament in Napa, Calif., on Wed. October 14, 2015. Rory McIlroy tees off on the 18th hole, during the Fry's.com Pro-Am...
One year ago this week, Rory McIlroy played in the PGA Grand Slam in Bermuda. Those are the spoils of success: The four-man event is designed only for reigning major champions, and McIlroy was the freshly minted winner of the British Open and PGA Championship.
